    • Class com.heliosmind.modulehandler.ModuleMetadata extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      -3867228299678431682L

      • Serialized Fields

        • className

          java.lang.String className
          The full name of the master class of the module to be loaded.

          The full name is the package name followed by the name of the class. For example, the full name of the String class is: java.lang.String.

        • dependencies

          java.lang.String[] dependencies
          An array of all the dependencies of this class. These modules must be initialized before initialization of this class.

          These modules must be identified with the full name of their master class. For example, the full name of the String class is: java.lang.String.

        • optionalDependencies

          java.lang.String[] optionalDependencies
          An array of all the optional dependencies of this class.

          These modules may or may not be already initialized at the initialization moment of this module. Therefore, nothing should be done at the first initialization of this module. Instead, wait for the call of the method postInit() to be made to apply changes following the optional dependencies that are present (or not present).

          These modules must be identified with the full name of their master class. For example, the full name of the String class is: java.lang.String.
